==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ungird
<hw>Un*gird"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>gird</ets>.]</ety> <def>To loose the girdle or
band of; to unbind; to unload.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He <qex>ungirded</qex> his camels.</q> <rj><qau>Gen. xxiv.
32.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ungive</ent>⟦br⟧
